 in PHP?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli value=\"6\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhat are sessions and cookies in PHP?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli value=\"7\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhat are the advantages of using PHP?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli value=\"8\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow does PHP handle error handling?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli value=\"9\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhat is a PHP function?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli value=\"10\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhat is the difference between \u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003ccode\u003e\u003cstrong\u003einclude()\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e and \u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003ccode\u003e\u003cstrong\u003erequire()\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e in PHP?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ol\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://media.geeksforgeeks.org/wp-content/uploads/20240619165724/PHP-Interview-Questions-and-Answers-(2024)-copy.webp\" alt=\"PHP-Interview-Questions-and-Answers-(2024)-copy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"470\" srcset=\"https://media.geeksforgeeks.org/wp-content/uploads/20240619165724/PHP-Interview-Questions-and-Answers-(2024)-copy.webp 1000w,https://media.geeksforgeeks.org/wp-content/uploads/20240619165724/PHP-Interview-Questions-and-Answers-(2024)-copy-100.webp 100w,https://media.geeksforgeeks.org/wp-content/uploads/20240619165724/PHP-Interview-Questions-and-Answers-(2024)-copy-200.webp 200w,https://media.geeksforgeeks.org/wp-content/uploads/20240619165724/PHP-Interview-Questions-and-Answers-(2024)-copy-300.webp 300w,https://media.geeksforgeeks.org/wp-content/uploads/20240619165724/PHP-Interview-Questions-and-Answers-(2024)-copy-660.webp 660w,https://media.geek